overview: The second installment in the Thereabouts films series, 'Reprise' see's brothers Gus and Lach back in the saddle for a 600 mile journey across the Colorado Rockies. This time, the pair are joined by mates, Cam Wurf (AUS) and Taylor Phinney (USA) for an under prepared, weather beaten journey through the mountains and into the Utah desert.
title: Thereabouts Reprise
